<%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>

  <div class="container py-5 working-page animate-on-scroll">
    <div class="text-center mb-5 pb-3">
      <h1 class="display-6 fw-bold">How Briefly Works</h1>
      <p class="lead text-muted max-w-lg mx-auto">
        From raw conversation to structured outcomes—without lifting a finger.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="step-card h-100">
          <div class="step-number">01</div>
          <h5 class="fw-bold mt-3">Runs in the Background</h5>
          <p class="text-muted mt-2 mb-0">
            The moment your meeting starts, Briefly begins listening through system audio. No bots joining the call,
            just a silent layer capturing context.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="step-card h-100">
          <div class="step-number">02</div>
          <h5 class="fw-bold mt-3">Understands Context</h5>
          <p class="text-muted mt-2 mb-0">
            Conversations are transcribed instantly. Decisions, action items, and key discussions are tagged the moment
            they’re spoken.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="step-card h-100">
          <div class="step-number">03</div>
          <h5 class="fw-bold mt-3">Visual Memory</h5>
          <p class="text-muted mt-2 mb-0">
            Important visuals like slides or diagrams are automatically captured with timestamps—so nothing is lost
            beyond words.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="step-card h-100">
          <div class="step-number">04</div>
          <h5 class="fw-bold mt-3">Live Dashboard Updates</h5>
          <p class="text-muted mt-2 mb-0">
            A live dashboard shows a running summary and evolving task list, giving everyone a shared understanding of
            progress in real time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="step-card h-100">
          <div class="step-number">05</div>
          <h5 class="fw-bold mt-3">Structured Output</h5>
          <p class="text-muted mt-2 mb-0">
            Once the meeting ends, Briefly generates a complete summary including open questions, and personalized
            action items.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="step-card h-100">
          <div class="step-number">06</div>
          <h5 class="fw-bold mt-3">Historical Tracking</h5>
          <p class="text-muted mt-2 mb-0">
            Across meetings, recurring unresolved topics are tracked and surfaced—revealing blockers before they become
            problems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>